Question: One image shows a dog in a bright colored collar gazing to one side, and the other image shows a dog reclining on something soft.

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image show a dog in a bright colored collar gazing to one side?')

ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image show a dog reclining on something soft?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the image show a dog reclining on something soft?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} xor {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} xor {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
